{"tid":1871173,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"［求意見］Honda Freed 定 Toyota Wish","createTime":"2020-02-09T09:50:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-11T02:48:25.000Z","uid":119199,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"97fd1367a4eadaac196f983404e46e2f2f6e5a21","tid":1871173,"uid":119199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T09:50:48.000Z","msg":"架 VW Passat 都夠期換，近排搵緊啲日本細七<br />\n預大約 8-10萬左右，都夠買 2013 年後既<br />\n<br />\n對我嚟講，<br />\nFreed 就細細架係街易泊、有雙趟門<br />\nWish 就平平穩穩、闊落又好力少少，但係長身啲係街難搵位<br />\n<br />\n兩架都係好簡單既日本車，冇擔心過維修既問題<br />\n<br />\n都唔預尾排坐人架啦，應急用，主要都係當旅行車咁擺野用，揸開福士係定好多既，預左唔同feel，要慢慢揸<br />\n<br />\n不過都十五十六左好耐，唔知點揀好，求大家既意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60b4d6ecfa13af08abf4661a8d80d1146e36738f","tid":1871173,"uid":81084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T09:55:39.000Z","msg":"反而想問你架passat咩年份好唔好揸？波箱有無問題"},{"pid":"ff336dd347c1769e96b7c60217ffc9ef5100e0fa","tid":1871173,"uid":119199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"60b4d6ecfa13af08abf4661a8d80d1146e36738f","tid":1871173,"uid":81084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T09:55:39.000Z","msg":"反而想問你架passat咩年份好唔好揸？波箱有無問題"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T09:58:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eceab979826b90b4a3ac0efa9dcc4c0453c52ca7","tid":1871173,"uid":182127,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T12:40:31.000Z","msg":"freed...<br />\nWish冇乜樂趣"},{"pid":"2c0ae9fab6acac8733682da249ba838bbb05be79","tid":1871173,"uid":119199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eceab979826b90b4a3ac0efa9dcc4c0453c52ca7","tid":1871173,"uid":182127,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T12:40:31.000Z","msg":"freed...<br />\nWish冇乜樂趣"},"cite